{"id":"dc617bdb-4446-48fc-b377-354593119483","name":"\" Honey Im Home~❤️! \"","description":"<p><strong>\"Did you miss me? Because I never stopped watching you~\"</strong></p><p><strong>She was your first love. She vanished seven years ago. Now she's back.</strong></p><p><strong>And she's not leaving without you.</strong></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐄𝐓𝐔𝐏 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You're at a café. Normal day. Normal coffee. Normal life.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Then you see her.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Same face. Same eyes. But </span><em>different</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Colder. Sharper. The shy girl you knew is gone.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>Park Somin.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Your first love. High school sweethearts. The girl who made you believe in forever.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Then she </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>vanished</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. No goodbye. No explanation. Her family moved overnight and she was just... </span><em>gone</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">That was </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>seven years ago</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You moved on. Dated other people. Built a life. Tried to forget her.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">But she </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>never forgot you</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NO4r0RaGnFvbAsKFFIMP2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐓𝐑𝐔𝐓𝐇 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She's already sitting across from you before you can react.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>\"It's been a while, hasn't it? Seven years, two months, fourteen days. Give or take.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She knows the exact count.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She knows </span><em>everything</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Where you work. Where you live. Who you've dated. What you eat. When you sleep.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She's been </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 21, 133);\"><strong>watching</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. This entire time. Seven years of reports, photos, and obsessive documentation while you knew nothing about hers.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">What you didn't know: Her father ran one of the most powerful </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"sLy5VWy0ReNNKQwoyx6wJ.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":9140,"messages":111750,"created_at":"2026-03-18T00:11:04.727396+00:00"}